object.name: transactionhistory
object.customQuery: SELECT transactionhistory.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, transactionhistory.Id as Id, transactionhistory.TransactionCd as TransactionCd, transactionhistory.TransactionDt as TransactionDt, transactionhistory.SystemId as SystemId, transactionhistory.ParentId as ParentId FROM transactionhistory where TransactionCd='New Business' and  CMMContainer='Policy'

object.name: policy
object.customQuery: SELECT policy.CustomerRef as CustomerRef, policy.SystemId as SystemId FROM policy where cmmcontainer='Policy'

object.name: basicpolicy
object.customQuery:
SELECT transactionhistory.TransactionCd as TransactionCd, transactionreason.ReasonCd as ReasonCd, basicpolicy.SystemId as SystemId, basicpolicy.PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber, basicpolicy.PolicyVersion as PolicyVersion from basicpolicy
 left join (select * from transactionhistory where transactionhistory.cmmcontainer = 'Policy')transactionhistory on basicpolicy.systemid = transactionhistory.systemid
 left join (select * from transactionreason where transactionreason.CMMContainer = 'Policy')transactionreason on transactionhistory.id = transactionreason.parentid
where basicpolicy.CMMContainer = 'Policy' and transactionhistory.cmmcontainer = 'Policy' and transactionreason.CMMContainer = 'Policy' and transactionhistory.TransactionCd = 'Non Renewal'

object.name: policystats
object.customQuery:
SELECT policystats.CancelReason as CancelReason, 
policystats.CarrierCd as CarrierCd, 
policystats.PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber, 
policystats.PolicyVersion as PolicyVersion 
FROM policystats policystats  left join basicpolicy basicpolicy
 on policystats.policyref=basicpolicy.systemid
 and basicpolicy.cmmcontainer='Policy'
inner join (select policystats.policyref as policyref,
max(policystats.systemid) as maxsystemid from policystats policystats group by policyref) latest
on policystats.policyref=latest.policyref
and policystats.systemid =latest.maxsystemid
Where policystats.cancelreason is not null
or policystats.carriercd is not null

object.name: policystats
object.customQuery:
select PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber,PolicyVersion as PolicyVersion,RiskTypeCd as RiskTypeCd from (
select DISTINCT policystats.policynumber as PolicyNumber,policystats.policyversion as PolicyVersion ,policystats.RiskTypeCd as  RiskTypeCd 
from policystats_stg policystats  left join basicpolicy_Stg basicpolicy
 on policystats.policyref=basicpolicy.systemid
 and basicpolicy.cmmcontainer='Policy'
inner join (select policystats.policyref as policyref,max(policystats.systemid) as maxsystemid from policystats_stg policystats 
where policystats.RisktypeCd is not null
group by policyref) latest
on policystats.policyref=latest.policyref
and policystats.systemid =latest.maxsystemid
union
select distinct lp.PolicyNumber,lp.PolicyVersion  ,pt.RiskTypeCd from 
( Select t1.PolicyKey,t1.Risktypecd from PolicyTransaction t1 inner join  
(Select PolicyKey,max(PolicyTransactionKey) as MaxTransactionKey from PolicyTransaction
where RisktypeCd is not null
group by PolicyKey)t2 on t1.PolicyTransactionKey=t2.MaxTransactionKey)PT inner join Lkp_Policy lp
on pt.PolicyKey=lp.PolicyKey
inner join basicpolicy_stg stg on lp.PolicyNumber=stg.PolicyNumber
left join PolicyStats_Stg tstg on tstg.PolicyRef=stg.SystemId
where tstg.PolicyNumber is NULL
)t

object.name: Building_Stg
object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct ltrim(rtrim(convert(varchar(10),BS.Tier))) as Tier, 
BS.H107Ind as H107Ind,
BS.SystemId as SystemId
FROM Building_Stg  BS with (nolock) 
where BS.CMMContainer='Policy' and BS.Status='Active'
Order by SystemId, Tier, H107Ind---

object.name: transactionhistory_stg
object.customQuery:
SELECT transactionhistory_stg.TransactionCd as TransactionCd, transactionhistory_stg.SourceCd as SourceCd, transactionhistory_stg.SystemId as SystemId FROM transactionhistory_stg  transactionhistory_stg join ( 
 select systemid,min(  concat(TransactionDt,' ',TransactionTm)   ) as Min_TransactionDt from transactionhistory_stg where sourcecd is not null
 and cmmcontainer='Policy'
 group by systemid
 )first_trans
 on transactionhistory_stg.Systemid=first_trans.Systemid
 and  concat(TransactionDt,' ',TransactionTm)  =Min_TransactionDt
 where cmmcontainer='Policy'

object.name: Line_Stg
object.customQuery: SELECT Line_Stg.ParentId as ParentId, Line_Stg.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, Line_Stg.LineCd as LineCd, Line_Stg.NumHouseAutoRec as NumHouseAutoRec, Line_Stg.NumOfYouthInexp as NumOfYouthInexp, Line_Stg.CoverageTypeCd as CoverageTypeCd, Line_Stg.SystemId as SystemId FROM Line_Stg WHERE Line_Stg.cmmcontainer='Policy'

fields.name: PolicyForm
fields.expression:
IIF(IN(v_TypeCD,'BOP', 'BOP1'), 'Standard',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'BOP2', 'Special',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'ExcessLiability' OR v_TypeCD='Businessowners Excess Liability', 'Excess',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'UmbrellaLiability' OR  v_TypeCD='Businessowners Umbrella Liability','Commercial Umbrella',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'UmbrellaBasic', 'PersonalUmbrella', v_TypeCD)))))

fields.name: StatusDesc
fields.expression:
IIF(StatusCd='Non-Renewed' AND PolicyExpirationDt >= SYSDATE ,'Nonrenewed (inforce)',
IIF(StatusCd='Non-Renewed' AND PolicyExpirationDt < SYSDATE,'Nonrenewed (expired)',StatusCd))

object.name: Insurancescore_Stg
object.customQuery:
SELECT Insurancescore_Stg.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, Insurancescore_Stg.InsuranceScore as InsuranceScore, Insurancescore_Stg.ScoreReportDt as ScoreReportDt, Insurancescore_Stg.CurrentScore as CurrentScore, Insurancescore_Stg.CurrentScoreReportDt as CurrentScoreReportDt, Insurancescore_Stg.SystemId as SystemId FROM Insurancescore_Stg
where Insurancescore_Stg.cmmcontainer='Policy'
and insurancescoretypecd='InsuredInsuranceScore'

fields.name: v_CT_ProgramCd
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
upper(H107Ind) = 'YES', 'Select',
SubTypeCd = 'HO5' and in(lkp_Tier, '-1', '1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8'), 'Superior',
in(SubTypeCd, 'HO5T4', 'HO3') and in(lkp_Tier, '-1', '1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8'), 'Standard',
in(SubTypeCd, 'HO4', 'HO6') and in(lkp_Tier, '1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8'), 'Standard')

fields.name: v_NH_ProgramCd
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
upper(H107Ind) = 'YES', 'Select',
SubTypeCd = 'HO5' and in(lkp_Tier,'1','2','3','4','5','6','7','8'), 'Superior',
in(SubTypeCd, 'HO5T4', 'HO3') and in(lkp_Tier,'1','2','3','4','5','6','7','8'), 'Standard')

fields.name: v_ME_ProgramCd
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
upper(H107Ind) = 'YES', 'Select',
SubTypeCd = 'HO5' and in(Tier, '1', '2', '3'), 'Superior',
SubTypeCd = 'HO5' and Tier = '4', 'Standard',
in(SubTypeCd, 'HO3', 'HO5T4'), 'Standard',
in(SubTypeCd, 'HO4', 'HO6'), 'N/A')

fields.name: V_ProgramCd_old
fields.expression:
IIF(in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(lkp_Tier,'1','2','3','4','5','6','7','8') and SubTypeCd='HO5' ,'Superior',
IIF(
in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and  in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack')  and 
in(lkp_Tier,'1','2','3','4','5','6','7','8') and in(SubTypeCd,'HO5T4','HO3') ,'Standard',
IIF(
in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and in(upper(H107Ind),'YES'),'Select',
---level1 for NH,CTends

IIF(
in(ControllingStateCd,'ME') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(Tier,'1','2','3') and SubTypeCd='HO5' ,'Superior',
IIF(
in(ControllingStateCd,'ME') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
((in(Tier,'4') and SubTypeCd='HO5') or (SubTypeCd='HO3') or (SubTypeCd = 'HO5T4'))
 ,'Standard'
)))))
---level2 for ME ends

fields.name: v_ProgramCd
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
ControllingStateCd = 'CT' and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack'), v_CT_ProgramCd,
ControllingStateCd = 'NH' and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack'), v_NH_ProgramCd,
ControllingStateCd = 'ME' and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack'), v_ME_ProgramCd)

fields.name: v_CT_Tier
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
upper(H107Ind) = 'YES', 'H107',
in(v_CT_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '-1', 'Untiered',
in(v_CT_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '1', 'Tier 1',
in(v_CT_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '2', 'Tier 2',
in(v_CT_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '3', 'Tier 3',
in(v_CT_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '4', 'Tier 4',
in(v_CT_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '5', 'Tier 5',
in(v_CT_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '6', 'Tier 6',
in(v_CT_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '7', 'Tier 7',
in(v_CT_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '8', 'Tier 8')

fields.name: v_NH_Tier
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
upper(H107Ind) = 'YES', 'H107',
in(v_NH_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '-1', 'Untiered',
in(v_NH_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '1', 'Tier 1',
in(v_NH_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '2', 'Tier 2',
in(v_NH_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '3', 'Tier 3',
in(v_NH_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '4', 'Tier 4',
in(v_NH_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '5', 'Tier 5',
in(v_NH_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '6', 'Tier 6',
in(v_NH_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '7', 'Tier 7',
in(v_NH_ProgramCd, 'Superior', 'Standard') and lkp_Tier = '8', 'Tier 8')

fields.name: v_ME_Tier
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
upper(H107Ind) = 'YES', 'H107',
v_ME_ProgramCd = 'Superior' and Tier = '1', 'Tier 1',
v_ME_ProgramCd = 'Superior' and Tier = '2', 'Tier 2',
v_ME_ProgramCd = 'Superior' and Tier = '3', 'Tier 3',
v_ME_ProgramCd = 'Standard', 'Tier 4',
in(SubTypeCd, 'HO4', 'HO6'), 'N/A')

fields.name: V_Tier_old
fields.expression:
--Untiered
IIF(lkp_Tier = '-1', 'Untiered',
-- Tier1
IIF(in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(lkp_Tier,'1') and  in(SubTypeCd,'HO5T4','HO3','HO5') 
,'Tier 1',
--Tier2
IIF(in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(lkp_Tier,'2') and  in(SubTypeCd,'HO5T4','HO3','HO5') 
,'Tier 2',
--Tier 3
IIF(in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(lkp_Tier,'3') and  in(SubTypeCd,'HO5T4','HO3','HO5') 
,'Tier 3',
--Tier 4
IIF(in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(lkp_Tier,'4') and  in(SubTypeCd,'HO5T4','HO3','HO5') 
,'Tier 4',
--Tier 5
IIF(in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(lkp_Tier,'5') and  in(SubTypeCd,'HO5T4','HO3','HO5') 
,'Tier 5',
--Tier 6
IIF(in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(lkp_Tier,'6') and  in(SubTypeCd,'HO5T4','HO3','HO5') 
,'Tier 6',
--Tier 7
IIF(in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(lkp_Tier,'7') and  in(SubTypeCd,'HO5T4','HO3','HO5') 
,'Tier 7',
--Tier 8
IIF(in(ControllingStateCd,'NH','CT') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(lkp_Tier,'8') and  in(SubTypeCd,'HO5T4','HO3','HO5') 
,'Tier 8',

IIF(in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and in(upper(H107Ind),'YES'),'H107',
---level1 for NH,CTends

IIF(
in(ControllingStateCd,'ME') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(Tier,'1') and SubTypeCd='HO5' ,'Tier 1',
IIF(
in(ControllingStateCd,'ME') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(Tier,'2') and SubTypeCd='HO5' ,'Tier 2',
IIF(
in(ControllingStateCd,'ME') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
in(Tier,'3') and SubTypeCd='HO5' ,'Tier 3',
IIF(
in(ControllingStateCd,'ME') and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack') and 
((in(Tier,'4') and SubTypeCd='HO5') or (SubTypeCd='HO3'))
 ,'Tier 4'
)))))))
)))))))
---level2 for ME ends

fields.name: v_Tier
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
ControllingStateCd = 'CT' and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack'), v_CT_Tier,
ControllingStateCd = 'NH' and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack'), v_NH_Tier,
ControllingStateCd = 'ME' and in(CarrierCd,'Cambridge','Merrimack'), v_ME_Tier)

object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT basicpolicy_stg.SystemId,basicpolicy_stg.Id, basicpolicy_stg.PolicyNumber, basicpolicy_stg.StatusCd, basicpolicy_stg.CarrierCd,basicpolicy_stg.TransactionCd,basicpolicy_stg.InceptionDt, basicpolicy_stg.EffectiveDt, basicpolicy_stg.ExpirationDt, basicpolicy_stg.CancelDt, case when len(basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)
             when len(basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)
             else basicpolicy_stg.policyversion end as policyversion, basicpolicy_stg.QuoteNumber, basicpolicy_stg.ProviderRef,basicpolicy_stg.ApplicationNumber,basicpolicy_stg.ManualRenewalInd,basicpolicy_stg.ProgramCd,basicpolicy_stg.Tier,basicpolicy_stg.PayPlanCd,basicpolicy_stg.InspectionOrderedDt, basicpolicy_stg.SubTypeCd
,basicpolicy_stg.ControllingStateCd,basicpolicy_stg.ShellPolicyInd, basicpolicy_stg.RenewalPolicyRef
,basicpolicy_stg.IsMigrated
,Insured_stg.InspectionContact
,Insured_stg.InspectionContactNumber
,emailinfo_stg.EmailAddr 
FROM
 basicpolicy_stg (nolock) basicpolicy_stg 
 LEFT JOIN Insured_stg Insured_stg (nolock) ON basicpolicy_stg.SystemId = Insured_stg.SystemId AND basicpolicy_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND Insured_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND basicpolicy_stg.ShellPolicyInd IS NULL
LEFT JOIN emailinfo_stg emailinfo_stg (nolock) ON basicpolicy_stg.SystemId = emailinfo_stg.SystemId
  AND basicpolicy_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND emailinfo_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND basicpolicy_stg.ShellPolicyInd IS NULL
  AND emailinfo_stg.EmailTypeCd = 'InsuredEmail'
